        Selling a Deceased Estate in Queensland: What the Executor Needs to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        From probate to settlement, the process of selling a deceased estate involves legal steps, beneficiary considerations, and tax implications that do not apply to a standard sale. Here is what executors need to understand.
      </p>
